{"tid":2276493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人口說抵制蘋果。身體卻很誠實","createTime":"2020-11-08T01:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T01:12:08.000Z","uid":72280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0754bb678f239f18df944114f0aaac9a0d677fd","tid":2276493,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:01:17.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】趙立堅：「如果美國真的禁用了微信，那麼蘋果手機，我們也可以不用用了。」 <br />\n<br />\n相隔約兩個多月，美國仍然未禁用微信，而在內地，蘋果手機仍有很多人選購。<br />\n<br />\n首輪發售的iPhone 12及iPhone 12 Pro上月中接受預訂首日，官網隨即預訂一空，京東蘋果旗艦店及蘇寧網購分別有超過120萬人預訂，過了三星期，現時上蘋果內地官網，每人仍然限訂購兩部，都要等到今個月最後一星期才能收貨。<br />\n<br />\n而第二輪發售的iPhone 12 Pro Max開始預售前一日，京東累計有超過九十萬人預約購買。<br />\n<br />\n我們在北京訪問蘋果用家，有否考慮轉用國產品牌。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果用家：「華為不是不能用谷歌嗎？小米給我的爸媽用挺好。（你自己就不用？）我不太會用，因為我用慣了蘋果，就不想用華為。」<br />\n<br />\n蘋果用家：「（有否想用小米？）沒有，從來沒有。（為甚麼？）我覺得蘋果在安全上是第一位。（華為及小米有甚麼進步才會考慮用？）也不會，不會考慮。（但是由中國人造的）你說甚麼？（不是國產嗎？）就算國產，還是跟產品各方面綜合性能，我覺得跟國產不國產沒有太大關係。」<br />\n<br />\n【首都專線】中美摩擦下民眾愛國仍愛「果」<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=411842&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411842%26refer%3DShare&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft252AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=0f19ac5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411842%26refer%3DShare&h=72ef2f10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=411842&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"be88dc8f136573651c55464f489c70efbefb62db","tid":2276493,"uid":72280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:02:07.000Z","msg":"蘋果用家：「華為不是不能用谷歌嗎？小米給我的爸媽用挺好。（你自己就不用？）我不太會用，因為我用慣了蘋果，就不想用華為。"},{"pid":"036ba2bf8bf05625aa15bb57dbea93f4c76ce4b5","tid":2276493,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T00:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7d53cab8f174803eb2d5b098d5b2dc5b558b73","tid":2276493,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T00:46:51.000Z","msg":"大陸閪d抵制得把口㗎姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZ7dm5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZ7dm5d.png&h=66445655&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fd6c1b8853f8ed0aabf6905d18487c906d780bc","tid":2276493,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:00:10.000Z","msg":"唔怕啦, 美利堅合眾省係自古以來中國不可分割的一部分<br />\n佢地只係用緊自己國家既產品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4914c2c12df4e8dd71ee94636e132ac9ffdae7a","tid":2276493,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:12:08.000Z","msg":"蘋果用家：「（有否想用小米？）沒有，從來沒有。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/201503/20150312182923_2_Untitled-15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F201503%2F20150312182923_2_Untitled-15.jpg&h=3c08cadc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}